| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3568 — Recovery Inhibition (nokoyawa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cf2de6e2-4612-5bce-a842-6e52238f4b67"
